LOCATION:Zoom
DESCRIPTION:In this installment of Best Practices in Medical Education Gran
 d Rounds\, Veronica Yan \, Ph.D.\, presents “Facilitators and Barriers to 
 Effective Learning.” Yan is an associate professor in the Department of Ed
 ucational Psychology within UT’s College of Education. Email Jennifer Brah
 am for the Zoom information. Best Practices in Medical Education Grand Rou
 nds is generously supported by the Massey Family Endowed Excellence Fund f
 or Dell Medical School.\\n\\nEvent page: https://dellmed.utexas.edu/events
 /best-practices-in-medical-education-grand-rounds-facilitators-and-barrier
 s-to-effective-learning
